div.p:
               Anſw. 1. When he ſhall ſhew me what that other price is with
which falſe teachers are bought, I ſhall believe him, and not before;
for it's not expreſt in Scripture.

Thus have I, as briefly as I could (and more briefly then the matter
indeed will well allow) ſpoken of redemption and reconciliation;
how general, and how ſpecial.

And if any ſhall ſay that the word in the Original ſignifies not a
Saviour, but a preſerver, and ſo conclude that the Father is the preſerver
of all men;
